    Operation

    public static enum Operation.Type
extends java.lang.Enum<Operation.Type>
    The order that operations are declared in this enumeration will determine their operation codes. Therefore, it is imperative that these enumerated constants stay in order. OperationCode names must be the same as the associated operation class simple name.
    Author:
    ashwin
